OL,3,CMurder suspect, 76, accused of killing
OL,4,Cfather-of-four refuses to attend court
OL,6,FNot guilty pleas have been entered on
OL,7,Fbehalf of a murder suspect accused of
OL,8,Fkilling a father-of-four in Tipton,
OL,9,Fafter he refused to attend a court
OL,10,Fhearing.
OL,12,F.A judge at Wolverhampton Crown Court
OL,13,Fordered that not guilty pleas to four
OL,14,Fcharges, including the murder of taxi
OL,15,Fdriver Harun Khan, are entered on
OL,16,Fbehalf of David Harrison.
OL,18,FHarrison, who's 76 and from Bilston,
OL,19,Fchose not to appear on a court video-
OL,20,Flink from HMP Frankland in County
OL,21,FDurham on Friday (10th April).
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
