OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776085870
OL,3,CMurder suspect, 76, accused of killing
OL,4,Cfather-of-four refuses to attend court
OL,6,FThe 15-minute hearing held in his
OL,7,Fabsence was told that he had notified
OL,8,Fthe court that he did not wish to
OL,9,Fattend.
OL,11,FHarrison is due to face trial before a
OL,12,FHigh Court Judge in November, charged
OL,13,Fwith murdering Mr Khan.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
