OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776085870
OL,3,CMurder suspect, 76, accused of killing
OL,4,Cfather-of-four refuses to attend court
OL,6,FMr Khan who was 39, was shot outside
OL,7,Fhis home in Tudor Street in Tipton
OL,8,Fnear Dudley at 9.25pm on March 3rd
OL,9,F2008, and taken to hospital.
OL,11,FHe was pronounced dead a short time
OL,12,Flater.
OL,14,FHarrison is also charged with
OL,15,Fwounding, after a 27-year old man was
OL,16,Fshot on Farthings Lane in Dudley on
OL,17,FDecember 14 2007, and also with two
OL,18,Fcounts of possessing a firearm with
OL,19,Fintent to endanger life.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
