FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776085870
OL,3,CMurder suspect, 76, accused of killing
OL,4,Cfather-of-four refuses to attend court
OL,6,FBefore adjourning the case after
OL,7,Fsubmissions from prosecutor Michael
OL,8,FBurrows KC and defence barristers
OL,9,FMichael Duck KC and Martin Liddiard,
OL,10,FJudge Michael Chambers KC said:
OL,12,F"The defendant has clearly not
OL,13,Fattended voluntarily on March 6th (a
OL,14,Fprevious hearing date) and, I am a
OL,15,Fsatisfied, not attended voluntarily
OL,16,Ftoday."
OL,18,FAfter directing that not guilty pleas
OL,19,Fbe formally entered on all four
OL,20,Fcharges, the judge added:
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776085870
OL,3,CMurder suspect, 76, accused of killing
OL,4,Cfather-of-four refuses to attend court
OL,6,F"I also propose that the defendant is
OL,7,Fwritten to by the court office, giving
OL,8,Fhim the warnings that would ordinarily
OL,9,Ffollow."
OL,11,FThe judge said the letter would
OL,12,Finclude notice of a right to give
OL,13,Fevidence, and that a trial may proceed
OL,14,Fin the defendant's absence.
OL,16,FA pre-trial review was also fixed to
OL,17,Ftake place on June 1st, with a
OL,18,Fdirection from the judge for Harrison
OL,19,Fto attend court in person.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@HO]
